{
  "page": "Raymun Fossoway",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\"><img alt=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/50px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/75px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/100px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Raymun Fossoway</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\"><img alt=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg/50px-House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg/75px-House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg/100px-House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Raymon_Fossoway.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Raymon Fossoway.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/55/Raymon_Fossoway.jpg/290px-Raymon_Fossoway.jpg\" width=\"290\" height=\"560\" srcset=\"/images/5/55/Raymon_Fossoway.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Raymun Fossoway, by Amok © <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.dabelbrothers.com/\">Roaring Studios</a></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nRaymun the Reluctant<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\">House Fossoway of Cider Hall</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\">House Fossoway of New Barrel</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Cider_Hall\" title=\"Cider Hall\">Cider Hall</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafraymun_fossoway.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafraymun_fossoway.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i> (appears)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nShaun Thomas</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_(TV_series)\" title=\"A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms (TV series)\">A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_-_Season_1\" title=\"A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms - Season 1\">Season 1</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Raymun Fossoway</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\">House Fossoway of Cider Hall</a>, who founded <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\">House Fossoway of New Barrel</a> some time after <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a>.\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Knight_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms_(TV_series)\" title=\"A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms (TV series)\">A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms</a></i>, Raymun is portrayed by Shaun Thomas.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Raymun\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Raymun</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Raymun\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Raymun</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raymun_Fossoway&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Raymun_Fossoway\" title=\"Category:Images of Raymun Fossoway\">Images of Raymun Fossoway</a></div>\n<p>Raymun was stocky, with a square face and a pug nose. He had short, wooly hair, and an engaging smile. He was a head shorter than <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Baratheon\" title=\"Lyonel Baratheon\">Lyonel Baratheon</a>, who was almost as tall as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> who was measured at 6'11\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Raymun was more honorable than his cousin, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Fossoway\" title=\"Steffon Fossoway\">Steffon Fossoway</a>. Steffon frequently reminded Raymun that he belonged to a junior branch of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway\" title=\"House Fossoway\">House Fossoway</a>, and often referred to him as \"an <a href=\"/index.php/Apple\" title=\"Apple\">apple</a> that's not ripe yet.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As a <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a>, he wore his own mail and plumed helm and sword. Raymun's shield initially bore the red apple of the Fossoways, but he painted it green after receiving <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knighthood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raymun_Fossoway&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Raymun_and_Steffon_Fossoway_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Raymun_and_Steffon_Fossoway_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg/350px-Raymun_and_Steffon_Fossoway_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"438\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Raymun_and_Steffon_Fossoway_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg/525px-Raymun_and_Steffon_Fossoway_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/Raymun_and_Steffon_Fossoway_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg/700px-Raymun_and_Steffon_Fossoway_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Raymun_and_Steffon_Fossoway_by_Even_Mehl_Amundsen.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Fossoway\" title=\"Steffon Fossoway\">Steffon</a> and Raymun Fossoway, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.evenamundsen.com/\">Even Mehl Amundsen</a> ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Raymun attended the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Ashford_Meadow\" title=\"Tourney at Ashford Meadow\">tourney at Ashford Meadow</a> as the squire of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Fossoway\" title=\"Steffon Fossoway\">Steffon Fossoway</a>, his older cousin, who promised to eventually <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Upon entering the tourney grounds, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> watched Steffon defeat Raymun in a spar. Noticing the <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a>, Steffon challenged Duncan to spar and Raymun urged him on, hoping for Duncan to win against his boastful cousin. Duncan declined to involve himself in their quarrel and, as Steffon challenged Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Grance_Morrigen\" title=\"Grance Morrigen\">Grance Morrigen</a> instead, Raymun caught up to him and apologized for urging him on against his cousin.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the final tilt of the first day, Raymun watched Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aerion_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerion Targaryen\">Aerion Targaryen</a> intentionally kill Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Hardyng\" title=\"Humfrey Hardyng\">Humfrey Hardyng</a>'s horse, much to his disgust. Spotting Duncan among the <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a>, Raymun sought him out and invited him to the Fossoway pavilion for wine. Raymun expressed his disgust for Aerion, and gave Duncan his opinion on the Targaryen princes and their personalities, believing Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Maekar_Targaryen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maekar Targaryen\">Maekar Targaryen</a> to be disgraced by his sons. The conversation was interrupted when Maekar's youngest, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Aegon Targaryen</a> disguising himself as Duncan's squire \"Egg\", burst into the Fossoway pavilion to seek out Duncan's help against Aerion, who was assaulting the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dornish\">Dornish</a> puppeteer <a href=\"/index.php/Tanselle\" title=\"Tanselle\">Tanselle</a>. Raymun warned Duncan against laying a hand against the prince, but Duncan intervened and attacked the prince. Raymun and Steffon arrived shortly after armed with their men-at-arms, while Aegon finally revealed himself as a prince to save Duncan's life.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Raymun took care of Duncan's horses while he was imprisoned at <a href=\"/index.php/Ashford_Castle\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ashford Castle\">Ashford Castle</a>, where Aerion challenged Duncan to a <a href=\"/index.php/Trial_of_seven\" title=\"Trial of seven\">trial of seven</a>. Returning to the Fossoway pavilion, Steffon pledged to join Duncan's side and left to seek out five more knights, though Raymun doubted Steffon's intentions. Raymun sought out additional knights with Aegon, fetching the wounded Humfrey Hardyng and his good-brother Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Beesbury\" title=\"Humfrey Beesbury\">Humfrey Beesbury</a>, seeking revenge against Aerion, while Aegon recruited Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robyn_Rhysling\" title=\"Robyn Rhysling\">Robyn Rhysling</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Baratheon\" title=\"Lyonel Baratheon\">Lyonel Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Upon the day of the trial, Steffon betrayed Duncan and sided with Aerion, who promised him a <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lordship</a>. Disgusted with Steffon, Raymun took his cousin's place. When Duncan hesitated in honoring Raymun's request to be knighted, Lyonel Baratheon intervened and granted knighthood on the youth, with Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Targaryen_(son_of_Daeron_II)\" title=\"Baelor Targaryen (son of Daeron II)\">Baelor Targaryen</a> filling the seventh slot. To avoid confusion with his cousin, Raymund repainted the red <a href=\"/index.php/Apple\" title=\"Apple\">apple</a> on his shield green, to the approval of Baelor. During the trial he fought Steffon, matching him blow for blow. Both left the field standing, with Raymun believing he broke a few of his cousin's ribs. After the trial, Prince Baelor asked Raymun for assistance in removing his helm, where it was revealed that the prince had been mortally wounded in the combat and promptly died in Duncan's arms.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\">House Fossoway of New Barrel</a>, the \"green-apple Fossoways\", was eventually recognized as a cadet branch of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\">House Fossoway of Cider Hall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafraymun_fossoway.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafraymun_fossoway.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Raymun\">Quotes by Raymun</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raymun_Fossoway&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Raymun\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Fossoway\" title=\"Steffon Fossoway\">My cousin</a> has promised to <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> me, but insists that I am not ripe yet.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Raymun, to <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I may not be ripe, but <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Fossoway\" title=\"Steffon Fossoway\">my good cousin</a> is rotten to the core. Knock the seeds out of him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Raymun, to <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Raymun</b>: If you think I wish any part of this, you're as thick as you are vile.<br />\n</p><p><b>Steffon</b>: Vile? Guard your tongue, Raymun. We're both <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\">apples from the same tree</a>. And you are my squire. Or have you forgotten your vows?<br />\n<b>Raymun</b>: No. Have you forgotten yours? You swore to be a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Steffon</b>: I shall be more than a knight before this day is done. <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">Lord</a> Fossoway. I like the sound of that.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Raymun and <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Fossoway\" title=\"Steffon Fossoway\">Steffon Fossoway</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I needed to make a small change to my sigil, lest I be mistaken for <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Fossoway\" title=\"Steffon Fossoway\">my dishonorable cousin</a>. I fear I am still not ripe ... but better green than wormy, eh?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Raymun, to <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Raymun\">Quotes about Raymun</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raymun_Fossoway&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Raymun\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Here's an <a href=\"/index.php/Apple\" title=\"Apple\">apple</a> that's not ripe yet.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Fossoway\" title=\"Steffon Fossoway\">Steffon Fossoway</a> to Raymun</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Raymun of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway\" title=\"House Fossoway\">House Fossoway</a>, in the name of <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Warrior (the Seven)\">the Warrior</a> I charge you to be brave. In the name of <a href=\"/index.php/Father_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Father (the Seven)\">the Father</a> I charge you to be just. In the name of <a href=\"/index.php/Mother_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Mother (the Seven)\">the Mother</a> I charge you to defend the young and innocent. In the name of <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Maiden (the Seven)\">the Maid</a> I charge you to protect all women.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-14\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Baratheon\" title=\"Lyonel Baratheon\">Lyonel Baratheon</a> to Raymun</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raymun_Fossoway&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span clas